<h3>Instructions </h3>
  <div style="height:100px; margin-top:20px">
      <div style="float: left">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-preheat-water.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 50px; margin-right: 30px"%>
    </div style="margin-top: 20px">

      <p style="margin-right: 50px">1. Preheat water and pour into press pot and desired drinking vessel to warm.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="height:100px; margin-top:20px">
      <div style="float: right">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-grind-beans.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 35px; margin-right: 50px"%>
    </div>

      <p style="margin-left: 50px">2. Measure beans on scale according to bean water ratio and grind beans in burr grinder. *(Remember to remove pre-heat water from vessels before adding coffee)</p>
  </div>

  <div style="height:100px; margin-top:20px">
      <div style="float: left">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-bloom-press.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 50px; margin-right: 30px"%>
    </div>

      <p style="margin-right: 50px">3. Tare press pot with beans on a scale. Pour enough water to cover all the beans, stir, and let bloom.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="height:100px; margin-top: 20px">
      <div style="float: right">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-immersion-press.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 35px; margin-right: 50px"%>
    </div>

      <p style="margin-left: 50px">4. Using the scale to measure, pour the remaing water ratio into the press pot and replace lid with plunger, but do not plunge.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="height:100px; margin-top:20px">
      <div style="float: left">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-plunge-press.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 50px; margin-right: 30px"%>
    </div>

      <p style="margin-right: 50px">5. After immersion time is finished, with control gently press down on plunger over 10-20 sec.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="height:100px; margin-top:20px">
      <div style="float: right">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-decant-press.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 35px; margin-right: 50px"%>
    </div>

      <p style="margin-left: 50px">6. Dispose of pre-heat water and decant brew from press pot into warmed vessel.</p>
  </div>
</div>

